Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:10.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The role of you young ones is not to fear failure, but to seek new frontiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:13.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,New frontiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:16.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"feather"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:22.11,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"china spoon"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.12,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"bowl"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:37.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shh...! If Naru hears this, it won't be a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were thinking of having a party for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:42.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're an adult, so a thousand yen should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:45.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're charging fees for a kid's birthday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not fees. It's to buy the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,With our allowances, we can't buy a whole cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:53.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-{\i1}nii{\i0} will be bringing food in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, get a present ready too, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Cake! Cake!\N--Hey, I've got to write today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:02.92,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"feather" "bowl" "china spoon"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's okay for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Onde"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:37.99,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Translation: Buddhist chanting and dancing"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got you a teddy bear for your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:44.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yaar! A punching bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got you a ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Perfect fer wrappin' 'round my waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,None of them feel right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What would make her happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, that cicada is noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:11.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I got the cicada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:16.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:23.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is about all I could come up with for a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Can you give me one of your beetles?\N--Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:29.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just one! Only one! I'll give you ten yen for it!\NThat's a lot of money to you kids, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yer so pesky, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yer talkin' bout a present fer Naru, right?\NI'm gonna be the one to give beetles to Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:42.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I'm gonna give her a hundred of these, and make a bed out of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:43.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"scuttle-scuttle"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's just torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:47.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna give her the same present as someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can see that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiro, Jiro? What are you guys bringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:55.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna give her candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you kids are all set...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You better think of what to get too, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get her a stag beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you can catch that many rhinoceros beetles, then stag beetles must be easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me your net.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's not takin' beetle catchin' seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,More like Sensei ain't takin' life itself seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Easy fer you to say!\NThey're hard ta find, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:25.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're as tall as an adult, you can see from above, so it'll be a cinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei can really get on your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm the one who found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yer too slow! Finders ain't keepers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna be so let down if ya can't even catch one beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a letdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care, but that's irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! There's another one over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose ta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:00.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I got the beetle--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't! The heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Lame! That's a drone beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei ain't gonna catch any!\N--Let's go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:11.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:14.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those brats! No way am I going to lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A giant stag beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:23.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Formation... Beta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little... more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,S-So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:33.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kenta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you kids doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I thought ya went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, say "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave without catching a single beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a cinch with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch any bug, no matter how high it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Got the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you lend me the net...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yer trying to catch 'em, and ya can't even touch 'em?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:08.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! They could bite or be carrying diseases!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They don't bite and they ain't diseased!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to the beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Up close, it looks creepier than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why's it so glossy?\NIt's no different from a roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a roach, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and hand me the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:22.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda think it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is he gonna be able to catch beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hercules beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why's it here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:45.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Musta got loose from a cage!\NNo way you could find one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:47.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Super good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:51.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They said on TV that it's worth twenty thousand yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty thousand for a bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Can I borrow the ladder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Let's work together to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna be so happy if we get her something super like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A kid's present worth twenty thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly, Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No... Can't reach it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Sensei!\N--Me?! N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hold the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Naru how great ya did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give her a super present together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Your best!\N--Do it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Big deal, just catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:40.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey, wait! Don't let go!\N--Her-cu-les! Her-cu-les!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can ya fall twice in one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:53.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being this big a klutz is almost like a talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to trust you kids again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Hercules beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't want it to get away, so I had the net clutched tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's... not movin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... dead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You squished him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you squished a Hercules beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Repent with yer life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:27.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do I deserve this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's just a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna give it to Naru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on! Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.05,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Hercules"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give ya one that I caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Cuz you did yer best for Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:05.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first adult who ever played with us so seriously, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a blast this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Me too!\N--Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it from the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Like this?\N--Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I can hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm one step closer to you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't playing with you kids.\NI just didn't want to lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be serious again, so be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are ya stupid?! Whaddya think yer doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:45.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... The place looks like it's ready for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Naru's 7 years old"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.75,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Happy Birthday Naru-{\i1}chan"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How did you girls get in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How long ya think it's been since we've used this place as our base?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:58.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this one, since I've still got one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:59.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A spare key.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting my bicycle key copied,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and since it was so cheap,\NI got five spares made for this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The door's open today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Hiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:17.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... If there are five, then who got the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was when I was playing in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei? Did you get a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... Present...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I brought her some bubble wrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up some peacock feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You girls sure know what'll click with Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you brought bubble wrap?\NI was thinking about that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--But those feathers are good too.\N--Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yup.\N--Well, I actually found these on the side of the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Everyone, get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:52.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thrown a birthday party before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you, we wouldn't have done this, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have one every year from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Get your crackers ready for when Naru comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah... Ah...\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! My birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, a present from Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, I'll go later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, just show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here. From Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.79,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"'I'll do anything you say' ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:36.79,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}1 time"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is this?! An elementary student's Mother's Day gift?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And only one?! So cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Naru. Go ahead and be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:58.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your happiness is starting to scare me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:12.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me, earnestly watering the sunflowers, not knowing who planted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably grow even if I don't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, climbing up there. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa's goin' grave visiting, so he said to bring you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grave visiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:27.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... It's already the Bon Festival period.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:38.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice of ya ta come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:43.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay for an outsider like me to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta go ta my fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:49.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was hopin' you'd keep watch over this grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Firecrackers?! That's so tasteless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal 'round these parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A custom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay! I'll leave ya to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:07.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's used to it, so just listen to what the kid has ta say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the fields're waitin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How irresponsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:14.49,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Kotoishi Family Grave"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:15.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really properly visited a grave before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:21.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who's at rest here, but please look after us for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we gotta light the {\i1}t o r o{\i0} first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--"Light the {\i1}t o r o{\i0} "?\N--Ya know, those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you mean the paper lanterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To r o{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it looks like every family has them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave the grave until the fire on this goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a candle meant to last for two hours?\NWe have to stay here that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we get bored, we got these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Going to pay my respects, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yasu-{\i1}ba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go and offer an incense stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was friends with Naru's grandma, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:03.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me. I managed to get through another year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds so glum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:10.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, dear. Must be tough in this hot weather, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:15.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, but having an unrelated person like me here must make Naru's grandma uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this candle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The flame's bobbing up and down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:23.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just means Grandma's looking at ya happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry, ya hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll make the owner of the grave happy, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:38.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You got a lighter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, parachutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're coming down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Midair catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:15:00.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Miwa-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Running wild without thinking about others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta say, its hard running in a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru wants ta do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! That was the last of them chutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei? C'mon, react a bit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring us is against the rules, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he wants us to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! I'll help! I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with those eyes!\NI feel like I'm going to be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this different from the\NBon festivities in the cities?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:33.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Completely different. In the first place, we don't pay a visit in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And no rice grains are offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:38.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No fireworks. No yukata.\NNo lining up lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! None of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it weird having the gravestone etched in gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! I thought gold was used everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:51.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I rarely pay my visits, so I can't speak proudly about customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:55.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Us either. We only ever come here during the Bon Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And we basically only come to play with fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And to see the Onde.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--The Onde?\N--'Scuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya mind if we pass through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Onde. People dance in front of graves less than a year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:32.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What does that translate to in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a foreign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Am I being stared at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I am being stared at! Did I do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should look at your face!\NYou freak out too easily, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:02.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you part of that group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to assist, since they didn't have enough guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We only got three more left. Stick it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you, Sensei.\NI need to dance a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:27.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I want to see you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei is really getting used to living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting like Naru's guardian too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried not to think too much about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:41.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...Sensei is on this island because he punched a prominent person in calligraphy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That means when he's forgiven...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did ya finish your summer assignments?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mind letting me copy 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-{\i1}chan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Sensei, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:06.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Smoky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I offer an incense stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Village Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's grandma took good care of me when she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the Kinoshita Shoten lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You mind if I offer an incense stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:24.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The hell ya doin', foolin' 'round here and leaving our family grave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please tell him that you forced me to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?! Hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:37.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-{\i1}chan{\i0}, what are you doing here?\NMom was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aki... How'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:44.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mom told me to give incense to Naru's grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I offer an incense stick this year too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's grandma sure is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.29,0:18:57.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, people keep coming here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:02.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps is always busy, so Naru's been keeping watch by herself all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen Naru's parents yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Pinwheel firecracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today is so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:22.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's usually boring waitin' for Grandpa, but tonight I don't wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just sleep here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:29.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya know, it must feel like this because you're here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! Naru wants ta play too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's always around other people when\NI see her, so I never realized it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:40.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...I guess she must get lonely like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:44.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably grow even if I don't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'll stay with her while I still have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... The fire went out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:20:01.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go already? Feels so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna go already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps hasn't come back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:09.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Yippie!\N--You're so kind, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Zip it!\N--Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru's gonna keep playin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:18.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:22.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma's happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:57.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Puchi-{\i1}san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.01,0:22:02.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to fish for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:05.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dogs don't eat crayfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:09.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking natural there, fishing at this here hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I still need work...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:14.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The people in the village seem to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How about just living here permanently already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:19.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:27.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as you have a place to call home, you're free to do as you desire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Puchi-{\i1}san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:36.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you become a big-time calligrapher, then treat me to lobster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}d o{\i0} eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:41.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this secret from Granny, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:47.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was still happy, even if it was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Puchi is a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:50.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
